# Skill routing (fijas)

Antes de implementar colas o APIs de fútbol:

- **Kafka** (topics, kafkajs, consumer groups, event streaming) → leer `~/.cursor/skills/kafka/SKILL.md`
- **RabbitMQ** (AMQP, exchanges, queues, amqplib, ack/nack, DLQ) → leer `~/.cursor/skills/rabbitmq/SKILL.md`
- **football-data.org** → `FOOTBALL_DATA_API_TOKEN` en env; cliente en `src/lib/football-data/`; docs https://www.football-data.org/documentation/quickstart
- **Seguridad**: nunca commitear tokens; solo `.env.local` / secrets del host
